italian-article-quiz
====================

An Android application quiz for learning the article of italian nouns

Title (en): Italian articles quiz

Description (en): The quiz consists of guessing the article of a Italian word. At every stage you will see a random Italian noun, and you can guess its article by clicking on the 4 buttons corresponding to the 4 singular determinative articles (il,lo,la,l'). The noun database contains 600+ basic words. While playing no internet access is required. 

Promo Text (en): Test your knowledge of Italian articles with this educational game.

Email: ghiottolino+ItalianArticleQuiz@gmail.com

